data.description:
Beautiful home in excellent location! This move-in ready 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch has an open floor plan and high-end upgrades. You will notice the thoughtfully designed split floor plan and natural light as you enter the home. The kitchen features quartz countertops and a striking subway tile backsplash that extends to the ceiling. Luxurious touches abound in both full bathrooms, featuring upgraded tile and vanities.

Step outside to a tranquil outdoor space in a fantastic neighborhood. Whether you prefer unwinding on the welcoming front porch, the back Trex deck in the fenced yard, or by the secluded fire pit, this home offers a retreat for everyone. 

Conveniently located within walking distance to the light rail, this neighborhood also connects to the Tobby Creek greenway trail system leading to UNC Charlotte and connecting to other parts of the greenway system.
